"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-life-style-team-usa-gymnastics-uniforms-paris-olympics-b2577548.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The 2024 Paris Olympic games will commence on July 26  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Team USA's gymnasticscompetitors are set to sparkle in crystal leotards at the2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 401, \"end\": 409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7733716620289844, \"rank\": 0.291009593445267, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 484, \"end\": 498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ahead of the highly anticipated games, which begin July 26, the one-of-a-kind uniforms for the US gymnastics team were revealed, debuting special adornments that pay homage to the host city.\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 596, \"end\": 598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999746754717797, \"rank\": 0.00016045294068844552, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the first time any of the Olympic gymnastics uniforms have been shown ahead of the games.\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 789, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"USA Gymnastics and GK Elite unveiled the 2024 leotards that will be worn by Jordan Chiles,Simone Biles, Jade Carey, Hezly Rivera, Leanne Wong, Joscelyn Roberson, and Suni Lee during their on-mat routines.\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 791, \"end\": 805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999358806, \"rank\": 6.41167519574096e-11, \"text\": \"USA Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\"}, {\"begin\": 810, \"end\": 812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"score\": 0.9999999319570657, \"rank\": 6.622514510990259e-08, \"text\": \"GK\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\"}, {\"begin\": 913, \"end\": 919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Rivera\", \"score\": 0.999699355330322, \"rank\": 0.0003007347586784995, \"text\": \"Rivera\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Rivera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Rivera\"}, {\"begin\": 921, \"end\": 927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leanne_Battersby\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Leanne\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leanne_Battersby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leanne_Battersby\"}, {\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Roberson\", \"score\": 0.999999999994543, \"rank\": 4.213528610542108e-12, \"text\": \"Roberson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Roberson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Roberson\"}, {\"begin\": 957, \"end\": 965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Suni Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, the uniforms for the men's gymnastics competitors - Paul Juda, Stephen Nedoroscik, Brody Malone, Frederick Richard, and Asher Hong - were revealed, too.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1162, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1062, \"end\": 1071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Juda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paul Juda\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Juda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Juda\"}, {\"begin\": 1073, \"end\": 1091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Nedoroscik\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stephen Nedoroscik\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Nedoroscik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Nedoroscik\"}, {\"begin\": 1093, \"end\": 1098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicholas_Brody\", \"score\": 0.997106698864939, \"rank\": 0.002739520237724684, \"text\": \"Brody\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicholas_Brody\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicholas_Brody\"}, {\"begin\": 1099, \"end\": 1105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"score\": 0.7125699087375565, \"rank\": 0.40224599765277436, \"text\": \"Malone\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\"}, {\"begin\": 1107, \"end\": 1116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.837308676374074e-19, \"text\": \"Frederick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over 47,000 Swarovski crystals will be embroidered across the eight different styles of leotards, which athletes are welcome to choose from.\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1304, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Every crystal was carefully stitched on to the garments by GK Elite's Pennsylvania production team in the US.\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1414, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1364, \"end\": 1366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"score\": 0.9999999319570657, \"rank\": 6.622514510990259e-08, \"text\": \"GK\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\"}, {\"begin\": 1375, \"end\": 1387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pennsylvania\", \"score\": 0.9970446383146367, \"rank\": 0.002561448386822851, \"text\": \"Pennsylvania\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pennsylvania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pennsylvania\"}, {\"begin\": 1411, \"end\": 1413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999746754717797, \"rank\": 0.00016045294068844552, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the shimmering additives are inspired by old Hollywood glitz and the red, white, and blue hues are meant to motivate patriotic spirit, pearl detailing will also be incorporated as an ode to the \\\"City of Love.\\\"\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1467, \"end\": 1476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999828282854, \"rank\": 1.717158386197176e-08, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a July 10 press release, Matt Cowan, the CEO of Elite Sportswear, LP, the parent conglomerate of GK Elite expressed gratitude for the purposeful work put into crafting the 2024 uniforms.\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1666, \"end\": 1671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/R._Guy_Cowan\", \"score\": 0.9954871371898054, \"rank\": 0.004367429413443323, \"text\": \"Cowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/R._Guy_Cowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/R._Guy_Cowan\"}, {\"begin\": 1733, \"end\": 1735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"score\": 0.9999999319570657, \"rank\": 6.622514510990259e-08, \"text\": \"GK\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are excited to continue our partnership with USA Gymnastics and unveil our extraordinary designs for the gymnasts representing our country at the Olympics,\\\" Cowan said.\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1996, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1873, \"end\": 1887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999358806, \"rank\": 6.41167519574096e-11, \"text\": \"USA Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\"}, {\"begin\": 1985, \"end\": 1990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/R._Guy_Cowan\", \"score\": 0.9954871371898054, \"rank\": 0.004367429413443323, \"text\": \"Cowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/R._Guy_Cowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/R._Guy_Cowan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"GK has a decorated history as the world's leading apparel provider for competitive gymnasts and we take pride in having our brand worn on the sport's biggest stage.\\\"\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1998, \"end\": 2000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"score\": 0.9999999319570657, \"rank\": 6.622514510990259e-08, \"text\": \"GK\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA's male competitors will be fitted in red long johns that cover the feet and silver leotards.\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2165, \"end\": 2173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7733716620289844, \"rank\": 0.291009593445267, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Replicas of the eight leotards and the men's final shirt are being sold on GK Elite's website for fans attending any of the events or watching from home.\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2343, \"end\": 2345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"score\": 0.9999999319570657, \"rank\": 6.622514510990259e-08, \"text\": \"GK\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All of Team USA will don head-to-toeRalph Lauren for the opening and closing ceremonies.\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2430, \"end\": 2438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7733716620289844, \"rank\": 0.291009593445267, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In June, the brand revealed the planned ensembles for both men and women, including single-breasted wool blazers, oxford shirts, and classic tailored denim for opening festivities and moto-esque jackets, polo shirts, and white denim for closing celebrations.\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ralph Lauren is profoundly honored to define the look of the American delegation as they represent our country in one of the world's most celebrated and storied events,\\\" David Lauren, Ralph Lauren's chief branding and innovation officer said in theJune 18 official release.\", \"from\": 2772, \"to\": 3046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2773, \"end\": 2785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.8567974638948981, \"rank\": 0.16713697476900552, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}, {\"begin\": 2834, \"end\": 2842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999918779806339, \"rank\": 7.97193318902152e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2943, \"end\": 2955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\"}, {\"begin\": 2957, \"end\": 2969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.8567974638948981, \"rank\": 0.16713697476900552, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This summer, Paris is the backdrop where fashion and sport will collide on the world's stage with a global audience and that is an incredibly exciting proposition.\\\"\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3212, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3061, \"end\": 3066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999749889, \"rank\": 2.5222967471456933e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3265, \"end\": 3276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.163972652931727e-14, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"